ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of SYLVIE TESSIER of Toronto, Ontario, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Brock Smith.
